Entity Space

Event create_space
  NewEntry  Action perform_space_creation

Event update_space
  When status = Active    Action perform_space_update
  When status = Archived  Action reject_request

Event archive_space
  When status = Active    Action perform_space_archive
  When status = Archived  Action notify_already_archived

Event search_space
  When status = Active    Action perform_search
  When status = Archived  Action reject_request
